    <title>Attention Is All You Need</title>
    <summary>The dominant sequence transduction models are based on complex recurrent or convolutional neural networks. We propose a new simple network architecture, the Transformer, based solely on attention mechanisms, dispensing with recurrence and convolutions entirely.</summary>
    <author>
      <name>Ashish Vaswani</name>
